asset.hookText: Hi Kimo, I read your review on Hoover.com and I think we have the answer to your issue. The Dual Power is very lightweight and your carpet strokes will need to be more deliberate. I put together this quick video for you to help. Let me know if you have any more questions. I'm here for you. -Felicia
